history.content:
Dear Students,
The EECS Honors Program Info Session scheduled for Thursday 3/12 3:15-4pm in 380 Soda has been cancelled in order to continue efforts to reduce person-to-person contact due to CoronaVirus. Here are the info session slides, you can also find them in the EECS Honors Program webpage along with all the information about the program.
Please feel free to email me with any questions or concerns you may have at mejiavalencia@eecs.berkeley.edu or schedule a phone or in person appointment with me here.
***NEW application deadline: Wednesday, April 1st at 4pm***
